text: Mia Todorović (born 22 June 1990) is a Croatian national volleyball player. She played at the 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. and 2013 CEV Volleyball European Championship. She played for Žok Rijeka and OTP Banka Pula. == References == Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian volleyball players
